+    // vstpoc: Android/wine has no real monitor EDID, so m_metadata parses as
+    // all-zero ("Failed to parse display metadata, using blank"). Some apps
+    // (e.g. AmpliTube's DocView) treat zeroed display colorimetry/luminance as
